        "func": "var dt = 2/3600;\nvar fv = msg.payload || 0;\nvar v  = context.get('vol_Water_Flow_Meter_Inlet') || 0;\nv += fv * dt;\ncontext.set('vol_Water_Flow_Meter_Inlet', v);\nflow.set('vol_Water_Flow_Meter_Inlet', v);\nglobal.set('vol_Water_Flow_Meter_Inlet', v);\nmsg.instant  = fv;\nmsg.payload  = +v.toFixed(3);\nreturn msg;\n",
